These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
Pet: bird, ferret, chinchilla, lizard
Job: pilot, librarian, chef, manager
1. Pet:ferret is somewhere to the right of Pet:bird##5
2. Job:manager is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3
3. Job:pilot is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:lizard is somewhere to the left of Job:manager##5
5. Job:pilot == Pet:ferret##1
6. Pet:chinchilla == Job:librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet      | lizard  | bird | ferret  | chinchilla |
| Job   | chef | manager      | pilot | librarian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
Transport: train, snowmobile, taxi, motorbike
Flower: daffodil, poppy, rose, marigold
1. Transport:snowmobile is between Flower:daffodil and Flower:marigold##2
2. Transport:motorbike is somewhere to the left of Flower:marigold##5
3. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Flower:rose##1
4. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Flower:poppy is on the left of Transport:train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | motorbike | taxi | snowmobile   | train |
| Flower           | rose      | daffodil    | poppy | marigold      |

