.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
Birthday: july, march, january, october
Color: azure, grey, apricot, white
1. Birthday:march == Color:grey##1
2. Color:white is on the right of Birthday:march##1
3. Color:apricot is somewhere to the left of Color:azure##5
4. Color:azure is on the left or right of Birthday:january##3
5. Birthday:october is somewhere to the right of Color:white##5
6. Birthday:march is somewhere to the left of Color:apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday        | march | july | january     | october |
| Color   | grey  | white   | apricot | azure    |

